TO INSTALL:

NodeJS >= 0.6.5
SASS >= 3.2.1 (http://sass-lang.com/download.html)

#http://npmjs.org/
#Mac OS X: $ sudo npm install haml

#Ubuntu 10.10: sudo apt-get install libhaml-ruby1.8
#Ubuntu 11.04: sudo apt-get install ruby-sass
#Fedora 14:    yum install rubygems
#              gem install haml

$ sudo gem install sass
$ sudo npm install mime -g
$ sudo npm install libxmljs -g

TO BUILD:

$ cd build
$ node build.js

or for production mode

$ node build.js production
